The cross itself is made of gold, full of patterns and glowing blue elements. And on the sides and behind it, as well as from the side beams hang huge numerous semblances of tentacles in black, from the cross itself also oozes black liquid. In the background even farther away are also deserted hills and uplands. The cross itself and the area around it is illuminated by bright golden sunlight breaking through the clouds.
